Ingredient Delete Data Preservation
Removed destructive delete chain from Ingredient delete workflow.
No longer deletes:
ing_allergens
ing_diet_tags
during Ingredient delete.
Reason:
Deleted Ingredient records remain recoverable and retain complete metadata.
